'''Tutlayin titergiyin''' (neɣ '''tatergit''') d afurk n [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] ttwameslayent deg  [[Ṣṣeḥra]] n Tafriqt n umalu. Llant rebɛa n tutlayin:
* [[Tutlayt tamaheɣt|Tamaheɣt]]
* [[Tutlayt tamaceɣt|Tamaceɣt]]
* [[Tutlayt tamajeɣt|Tamajeɣt]] (neɣ Tayirt)
* [[Tutlayt tawellemt|Tawellemt]]

Tatergit tettemgerrad deg tama ɣer tayeḍ. Tatergit n [[Ahaggar|Uhaggaṛ]] (tin umi ɣɣaren tahaggaṛt neɣ tamaheɣt), ssawalen-tt deg wenẓul n Lezzayer. Tamaceq ssawalen-tt deg [[Mali]] g [[Aẓawad|Uẓawad]], ma d tamajeq/tayirt ssawalen-tt deg [[Nnijer]]. Tutlayt-a mazal tettwaru ar ass-a s ugemmay n tfinaɣ, maca, deg Nnijer ed Mali, llan wid ay tt-yettarun s ugemmay alatini. Tamaceɣt ssawalen-tt daɣen deg [[Libya]] akekd Burkina Faso, am wakken ay llan cwiṭ n Yimuhaɣ deg [[Nijirya]] d [[Ččad]].

